ue of H_0 presented in\nthis paper is comparable to recent measurements of H_0 from the gravitational\nlenses 0957+561, PG1115+080, B0218+357, and PKS1830-211.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Jul 1999 00:05:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-31"}
